-- American States Water Reports Higher Results for Third Quarter
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2012-11-05T13:42:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-05/american-states-water-reports-higher-results-for-third-quarter.html
American States Water Co. (AWR) , a
California-based water service and electricity provider,
reported third-quarter net income of $18.7 million, almost 20
percent higher than a year earlier.  Earnings per share for the period compared with a year ago
advanced 17 percent, the San Dimas-based utility said today in a
statement. Operating revenue for the quarter from the company’s
water and electric operations was $133.5 million, it said,
higher than analysts’ estimates of $124.4 million.  American States Water is the parent of Golden State Water
Company and American States Utility Services Inc. Its shares
have risen almost 25 percent this year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
